CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776250558
OL,3,CKiller bragged 'I stabbed him fully'
OL,4,Cafter murdering student on railway
OL,5,Ctracks
OL,7,FA fight broke out on the station
OL,8,Fplatform between two groups of men
OL,9,Fover a drug deal to pay #50 for 10
OL,10,FMDMA tablets, before Dondaldson chased
OL,11,FMr Gnaneswaran, 21, onto the tracks
OL,12,Fand stabbed him in the chest, abdomen
OL,13,Fand thigh.
OL,15,FHe was pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,17,FLess than an hour later, Donaldson was
OL,18,Fcaught on CCTV on an N87 night bus
OL,19,Fsmiling and laughing.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776250558
OL,3,CKiller bragged 'I stabbed him fully'
OL,4,Cafter murdering student on railway
OL,5,Ctracks
OL,7,FHe was also recorded on the audio of a
OL,8,Fdoorbell camera saying: "I stabbed him
OL,9,Fthrough the back bro, I stabbed him
OL,10,Ffully.
OL,12,FI watched it and I felt it go in him,
OL,13,Fyeah."
OL,15,FHe was arrested at his home in west
OL,16,FLondon on January 11 2024 where he was
OL,17,Fdiscovered hiding in a cupboard.
OL,19,FPolice found 74 wraps of crack and
OL,20,Fheroin in his bedroom with a street
OL,21,Fvalue of more than #1,000.
OL,26,@pD@YOUuD@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776250558
OL,3,CKiller bragged 'I stabbed him fully'
OL,4,Cafter murdering student on railway
OL,5,Ctracks
OL,7,FFollowing the unanimous verdict at the
OL,8,FOld Bailey, Judge Angela Rafferty KC
OL,9,Fremanded the defendant in custody and
OL,10,Fadjourned sentencing to a date to be
OL,11,Ffixed.
OL,13,FBritish Transport Police Detective
OL,14,FChief Inspector Paul Attwell said:
OL,15,F"What started as an argument over a
OL,16,Fdrug deal ended in a young man's life
OL,17,Fbeing cut short by a remorseless thug.
OL,19,F"Donaldson showed his true colours as
OL,20,Fa coward by arming himself with a
OL,21,Fknife that night.
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776250558
OL,3,CKiller bragged 'I stabbed him fully'
OL,4,Cafter murdering student on railway
OL,5,Ctracks
OL,7,F"His cowardice has continued by never
OL,8,Faccepting responsibility and admitting
OL,9,Fhis crime ` thankfully the jury saw
OL,10,Fthrough his lies.
OL,12,F"While no verdict can ever compensate
OL,13,Ffor the loss of Anojan, I hope today's
OL,14,Foutcome provides his family with some
OL,15,Fsense of closure.
OL,17,F"Thanks to our extensive
OL,18,Finvestigation, justice has now been
OL,19,Fserved to the man responsible for
OL,20,Fkilling their loved one."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
