PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776250558
OL,3,CKiller bragged 'I stabbed him fully'
OL,4,Cafter murdering student on railway
OL,5,Ctracks
OL,7,FMr Gnaneswaran's family paid tribute
OL,8,Fto a "much-loved son and brother".
OL,10,FIn a statement issued through British
OL,11,FTransport Police, they said: "Anojan
OL,12,Fwas in his third year at university
OL,13,Fstudying accounting and finance, and
OL,14,Fhe was so excited for his future.
OL,16,F"He excelled at all sports and had
OL,17,Fachieved first-dan black belt in
OL,18,Fkarate ` he competed in the World and
OL,19,FEuropean championships in karate, and
OL,20,Fwe will all miss him so much."
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@aO]sD@^OUxD@AOU|D@^O]
